<doc id="310328" wikidata="Q404006" url="?curid=310328" title="Sail (disambiguation)">
<text>A [[sail]] is any type of surface intended to move a vessel, vehicle or rotor by being placed in a wind.

Sail or SAIL may also refer to:

==Arts and entertainment==
* &quot;A Sail&quot;, a poem by Mikhail Lermontov
